======= Email OTP login ===
=======How to use =====
1) Clone Project
2) Create databse called "Github_type_OTP_Login_System" and import SQL file which is in DBFile folder.
3) Run Following URL:http://localhost/Github_type_OTP_Login_System/

=====Special Feature====
1) No need to button clicking for OTP Verification
2) Email sent via local machine so you can set up some functionality for local mail and get email by localhost. 